msgctxt "308_Dealer"
msgid "Welcome to the blackjack table. You can play one game for as little as 10 chips. Care to try your luck?"
msgstr "Bienvenido a la mesa de blackjack. Puedes jugar una partida con tan solo 10 fichas. ¿Te animas a probar suerte?"

msgctxt "320_Dealer"
msgid "I've noticed that you play blackjack quite often. Would you be interested in playing the house, one-on-one?"
msgstr "He notado que juegas blackjack con frecuencia. ¿Te interesaría enfrentarte a la casa, uno contra uno?"

msgctxt "332_Dealer"
msgid "What would you like to do now?"
msgstr "What would you like to do now?"

msgctxt "344_Dealer"
msgid "All right, then. First, I'll need your 1,000 chips."
msgstr "De acuerdo. Primero necesitaré tus 1,000 fichas."

msgctxt "368_Dealer"
msgid "Thank you. Now, then, let's begin."
msgstr "Gracias. Ahora, comencemos."

msgctxt "392_Dealer"
msgid "Very well. Let's continue with normal blackjack, then."
msgstr "Perfecto. Continuemos con el blackjack normal, entonces."

msgctxt "416_Dealer"
msgid "Sure, I'm feeling lucky today."
msgstr "Claro, hoy me siento afortunado."

msgctxt "428_Dealer"
msgid "Very good, sir."
msgstr "Muy bien, señor."

msgctxt "464_Dealer"
msgid "Not right now."
msgstr "Ahora no."

msgctxt "476_Dealer"
msgid "Very well. We hope you'll play with us next time."
msgstr "Muy bien. Esperamos que vuelvas a jugar con nosotros."

msgctxt "488_Dealer"
msgid "You seem to be short on chips. Please visit us again soon."
msgstr "Parece que te faltan fichas. Vuelva a visitarnos pronto."

msgctxt "500_Player"
msgid "Tell me the rules."
msgstr "Explícame las reglas."

msgctxt "512_Dealer"
msgid "This is a game between you and the house. Whoever gets three wins first wins the game."
msgstr "Este es un juego entre tú y la casa. El primero que gane tres rondas, gana la partida."

msgctxt "524_Dealer"
msgid "Before the game begins, I'll need 1,000 chips for you to join. The payout differs depending on which deck is used."
msgstr "Antes de comenzar, necesitaré que aportes 1,000 fichas para participar. El pago varía según el tipo de baraja que se use."

msgctxt "536_Deck Type and Payout"
msgid "Standard Deck: 2,000 chips\\r\n"\n"Without 2/3/4: 2,500 chips\\r\n"\n"Without 7/8/9: 2,000 chips\\r\n"\n"Without J/Q/K: 4,000 chips"
msgstr "Baraja estándar: 2,000 fichas\\r\n"\n"Sin 2/3/4: 2,500 fichas\\r\n"\n"Sin 7/8/9: 2,000 fichas\\r\n"\n"Sin J/Q/K: 4,000 fichas"

msgctxt "548_Dealer"
msgid "These are the payouts for winning against me one-on-one."
msgstr "Estos son los premios por ganarme en un duelo cara a cara."

